Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sono a casa! Ma cosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papà, oggi non dovevi andare\Nal concerto di Yoko Okino?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:30.30,Default - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Calze! {\alpha&HFF&}Calze!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insomma, papà...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:31.50,Default - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Calze! Calze!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:32.06,Default - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Cravatta! {\alpha&HFF&}Cravatta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fa' attenzione!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:32.89,Default - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Cravatta! Cravatta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giacca!{\alpha&HFF&} Giacca!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giacca! Giacca!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Biglietto!{\alpha&HFF&} Biglietto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Biglietto! Biglietto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.12,0:02:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E poi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... attento alle scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Per favore! Mi accompagni\Nal concerto di Yoko Okino!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oggi è l'ultimo giorno del tour...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lei si è rotto una gamba,\Nquesta è un'ambulanza, non un taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko! Che male!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\bord1\fs23\c&HA2A339&\3c&H545147&\pos(331.362,131.6)\frx26\fry0}Ospedale di Beika
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Com'è grande quest'ospedale!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai ragione.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In che stanza l'hanno messo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Non lo so. Vado a chiedere all'accettazione.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanno detto che è nella 503!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bene, andiamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.25,Cartello BASE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)\fnComic Sans MS\fs23\b1\i1\c&H181518&\pos(318.857,194.286)\blur0.5}Daisaburo Sekiguchi
